&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;output_path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;test/data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Most of the config isn&amp;rsquo;t that interesting, except the output_path will be used to determine where the newly generated
dashboards will be. Make sure you have a valid configuration before continuing.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>